PrecisRe-appointment, effective October 5, 1992, of Michel Latraverse, of Montreal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Copyright Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years ending on October 4, 1994, or, if the Board is dissolved, on the date of the dissolution, whichever date is earlier.
